cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.CV, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the use of recurrent neural networks for molecular generation, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the properties of the generated molecules, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and computational engineering (cs.CE). Additionally, the use of SMILES encoding for the existing compounds and the assessment of synthesizability could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL).
